{
  "stem": "26792.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you can get a Latvian passport in Gondinger. said, if this old lady can carry stones in this hot July sun, I can, too.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am 100% Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father is a Jew, and my mother is a Jewess.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, this is what they sometimes tried to do, to pick out girls whom they liked, and perhaps temporarily, I don't know, and not provide a passport to live in town, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Were you called to the prefecture?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was not called.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of the days, when we were working in the old city of Riga, they took us for a change to a different place.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was one of the horror places, like the Perkonkrust.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the police headquarters in Riga, in the center of the city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There we were also asked to clean.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Women were asked to clean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The men disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And while I was cleaning the window, I saw terrible sights.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the suburbs of Riga, there was very many rich Jews left, rich and intelligentsia of the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some of them were dragged to the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were beaten to death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were lying in their pool of blood, which I saw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they were--they spilled cold water on them in order to revive them, and to beat them again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the terrible shrieks and yelling from all the parts of the prefectura.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And unfortunately, the Russian prisoners of war shared our fate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were also sitting there and eating their crust of black bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know what happened to them, but we were there together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This-- there I saw a teacher, a former teacher of mine, even, one of the torturers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were all young Latvians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was no German there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
